1
00:01:37,540 --> 00:01:43,880
[My Bargain Queen]

2
00:01:43,880 --> 00:01:48,050
[Episode 2]

3
00:01:53,350 --> 00:01:56,030
- Excuse me, I have to answer a call.
- Sure.

4
00:01:56,030 --> 00:01:57,470
Hello, Hubby.

5
00:01:57,470 --> 00:01:59,850
You're here?

6
00:01:59,850 --> 00:02:00,910
I'm upstairs.

7
00:02:00,910 --> 00:02:03,330
Okay. I'll be there right away.

8
00:02:19,850 --> 00:02:22,120
Hubby, I'm here!

9
00:02:27,300 --> 00:02:29,690
Starting today,

10
00:02:29,690 --> 00:02:33,680
wherever you go,

11
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:36,480
I will go there, too!

12
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:39,830
Listen carefully,

13
00:02:39,830 --> 00:02:42,170
I'm not the type to pester,

14
00:02:42,170 --> 00:02:45,540
and I will not persuade you to stay. But if you take one more step today,

15
00:02:45,540 --> 00:02:47,570
one step, I will dump you.

16
00:02:47,570 --> 00:02:50,550
Even if you come back to me begging, I will not take you back.

17
00:02:50,550 --> 00:02:52,440
He Zhijuan!

18
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:59,780
[Xia Qian, I'm sorry! I cannot get engaged to you.

19
00:03:09,070 --> 00:03:11,690
Miss Xia, my fiancé is here to pick me up.

20
00:03:11,690 --> 00:03:15,040
Let me introduce you guys, He Zhijuan.

21
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:16,680
Sorry for arriving late.

22
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:19,100
Hello, I am He Zhijuan.

23
00:03:35,420 --> 00:03:37,840
What's wrong, Miss Xia?

24
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:40,480
I don't know. It's just...

25
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:43,400
just that my eyes are allergic.

26
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:46,640
Sorry, Miss Ning Meng, I have to go.

27
00:04:21,030 --> 00:04:22,790
Qianqian.

28
00:04:23,430 --> 00:04:24,790
Qianqian.

29
00:04:24,790 --> 00:04:26,890
- I'm so sorry
- I'm sorry.

30
00:04:37,390 --> 00:04:40,730
- Qianqian.
- You arrived?

31
00:04:40,730 --> 00:04:42,300
Qianqian.

32
00:04:42,300 --> 00:04:44,030
Sit down.

33
00:04:44,030 --> 00:04:45,760
Are you okay?

34
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:54,260
That's enough.

35
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:57,170
Are you okay?

36
00:04:57,170 --> 00:04:59,080
I feel much better.

37
00:05:00,910 --> 00:05:03,470
- Slow down, slow down.
- Shuangshuang,

38
00:05:03,470 --> 00:05:05,880
I still don't understand.

39
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,160
Help me come up with a reason.

40
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:11,690
What do you think is wrong with He Zhijuan?

41
00:05:11,690 --> 00:05:15,740
- Exactly.
- Do you think he was diagnosed with a terminal illness?

42
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:21,410
He must have his own reasons.

43
00:05:22,570 --> 00:05:24,880
Something bad happened?

44
00:05:24,880 --> 00:05:27,700
Something bad really did happen.

45
00:05:27,700 --> 00:05:30,420
No, no, no.

46
00:05:30,420 --> 00:05:34,210
I think it must be like how we discussed.

47
00:05:34,210 --> 00:05:36,770
At the time,

48
00:05:36,770 --> 00:05:39,840
I didn't give him the opportunity and time to explain.

49
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:42,280
He must have left in anger.

50
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:45,760
If he wanted to explain, he would have already explained. Right?

51
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:48,860
No? Never mind.

52
00:05:48,860 --> 00:05:53,360
Forget him. A man like him doesn't deserve your love.

53
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,520
He's worth it.

54
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:59,800
Let me tell you the truth, He Zhijuan is not that type of person.

55
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:03,230
I swear, He Zhijuan is not that type of person.

56
00:06:03,230 --> 00:06:05,840
I know him really well.

57
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:11,210
Did you know at the time he looked back at me?

58
00:06:11,210 --> 00:06:13,750
He looked at me. He wanted to say something.

59
00:06:13,750 --> 00:06:17,420
But I didn't give him time, so he left.

60
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:19,500
He will come back.

61
00:06:21,890 --> 00:06:23,910
But Shuangshuang,

62
00:06:25,070 --> 00:06:27,130
at the time...

63
00:06:28,650 --> 00:06:30,750
at the time...

64
00:06:31,770 --> 00:06:34,720
why did I say those words?

65
00:06:35,830 --> 00:06:40,560
I told him, if

66
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:42,740
he comes back,

67
00:06:44,570 --> 00:06:48,820
I will dump him.

68
00:06:48,820 --> 00:06:51,700
- Don't take him back. We don't want him.
- I want him.

69
00:06:51,700 --> 00:06:52,910
Yes, don't take him back.

70
00:06:52,910 --> 00:06:56,360
- I want him, I want him, I want him.
- Don't think about him.

71
00:07:03,630 --> 00:07:05,940
What are you doing?

72
00:07:06,810 --> 00:07:10,770
You aren't thinking I am going to get drunk because of He Zhijuan, right?

73
00:07:10,770 --> 00:07:14,340
I... just really never expected that

74
00:07:14,340 --> 00:07:17,490
we would meet again like that.

75
00:07:19,650 --> 00:07:21,930
What will you do next?

76
00:07:26,690 --> 00:07:28,930
That's such a coincidence.

77
00:07:28,930 --> 00:07:32,960
Do you think Ning Meng planned it on purpose?

78
00:07:36,220 --> 00:07:38,730
I don't think so.

79
00:07:38,730 --> 00:07:42,510
It felt like Ning Meng didn't know.

80
00:07:43,970 --> 00:07:48,690
How did He Zhijuan react when he saw you? You can't say that he didn't know.

81
00:07:52,090 --> 00:07:55,480
Lihe Capital has obtained 3% of Director Lin's shares.

82
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,860
Thank you for your work, Director Qin.

83
00:07:57,860 --> 00:08:02,020
Oh, wait. I should call you Vice GM Qin now.

84
00:08:02,790 --> 00:08:04,830
Six years ago, I brought you to Evergreen.

85
00:08:04,830 --> 00:08:07,490
I knew already at the time, with your ability,

86
00:08:07,490 --> 00:08:10,190
you would be able to earn that position.

87
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:12,830
It would not have been possible without the help of Director Xue.

88
00:08:13,490 --> 00:08:16,850
Whether or not Lihe Capital will be able to acquire Evergreen,

89
00:08:16,850 --> 00:08:19,820
all depends on Vice GM Qin.

90
00:08:21,140 --> 00:08:23,640
Please excuse me. I need to take this call.

91
00:08:27,230 --> 00:08:29,840
Hello, Mengmeng.

92
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:32,460
What's wrong? Is your brother mad at you again?

93
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:36,940
Come to my office, I will be there shortly.

94
00:08:37,490 --> 00:08:39,210
See you in a bit.

95
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:44,640
I'm sorry, Director Xue, Sheng Zhening's sister is looking for me. I will head back first.

96
00:08:44,640 --> 00:08:49,880
I did not realize that you get along quite well with both the brother and sister of the Sheng family.

97
00:08:51,250 --> 00:08:52,990
Hebo,

98
00:08:52,990 --> 00:08:57,580
it wasn't easy for you to get to this position, don't let your emotions lead you astray.

99
00:08:58,710 --> 00:09:01,400
Don't worry, I know what to do.

100
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:16,140
[Alipay]

101
00:09:19,830 --> 00:09:22,610
What does this mean? Why did you transfer money to me?

102
00:09:22,610 --> 00:09:27,020
We'll pool our money together to refund Ning Meng. Let's not take this case.

103
00:09:27,020 --> 00:09:29,680
Shuangshuang, let me tell you. That's really not necessary. I have money.

104
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:31,350
Don't tell me you have money.

105
00:09:31,350 --> 00:09:34,760
I already heard you sold your car.

106
00:09:35,350 --> 00:09:39,380
Yes, money needs to be made. But you shouldn't make it so hard on yourself.

107
00:09:39,380 --> 00:09:43,600
Besides, no matter what happens, I can support you financially.

108
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:51,020
Why are you smiling? I'm being serious.

109
00:09:51,020 --> 00:09:52,360
Thank you.

110
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:55,900
There is no need to say that between us. Please don't burden yourself.

111
00:09:55,900 --> 00:09:59,990
I am not burdened, I just really want to take this case.

112
00:09:59,990 --> 00:10:02,820
And it's not because of money.

113
00:10:02,820 --> 00:10:06,690
It's because, after He Zhijuan ran away from the engagement, I wanted to change.

114
00:10:06,690 --> 00:10:11,130
Under those tough circumstances, I forced myself to start my own company.

115
00:10:11,130 --> 00:10:14,720
We've worked really hard these past few years. We took all cases,

116
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:17,580
to make "Worth or Not" to where it is today.

117
00:10:17,580 --> 00:10:23,290
This is our dream. Why should we let go of the case because of He Zhijuan?

118
00:10:23,290 --> 00:10:25,840
Besides, he isn't important to me anymore.

119
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:29,990
Not important? Is that really how you feel?

120
00:10:31,330 --> 00:10:35,890
I am the person who understands the most about how much you suffered when He Zhijuan left you.

121
00:10:35,890 --> 00:10:41,170
You became a different person. Just to not think about him, you threw yourself into work. You worked like crazy.

122
00:10:41,170 --> 00:10:44,970
I don't want you to be like that again. Now that He Zhijuan is back,

123
00:10:44,970 --> 00:10:47,690
I am afraid you will become that person again.

124
00:10:47,690 --> 00:10:51,020
Shuangshuang, because He Zhijuan is back,

125
00:10:51,020 --> 00:10:54,280
I've seen him and now I understand.

126
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:59,600
It's been two years. He has his own life, I have my own.

127
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:03,220
We are not important to each other anymore.

128
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:07,670
It's true,

129
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:11,760
helping my ex-boyfriend schedule his wedding is ridiculous.

130
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:15,170
But what can I do? This ridiculous situation happened and I need to fix it.

131
00:11:15,170 --> 00:11:17,460
If I break the contract and not take this case,

132
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:19,900
it would mean that I have not forgotten him.

133
00:11:19,900 --> 00:11:24,830
So, we must take it. We must finish it beautifully.

134
00:11:24,830 --> 00:11:27,930
Come on, let's drink.

135
00:11:28,710 --> 00:11:30,690
Let's work hard.

136
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:56,140
What brings you here today?

137
00:11:56,140 --> 00:11:58,390
I miss Brother Hebo, of course.

138
00:11:58,390 --> 00:12:00,000
Miss me?

139
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:02,090
I thought you are busy dating and don't have time to miss me.

140
00:12:02,090 --> 00:12:03,990
Just tell me. What is it?

141
00:12:03,990 --> 00:12:08,530
Looks like I can't hide anything from you, Brother Hebo.

142
00:12:08,530 --> 00:12:12,880
Brother Hebo, I'm getting married. At the Evergreen Hotel.

143
00:12:14,610 --> 00:12:17,750
I thought your brother didn't want you to get married so early.

144
00:12:17,750 --> 00:12:19,120
You've talked him into it already?

145
00:12:19,120 --> 00:12:23,310
Of course not! You know my brother.

146
00:12:23,310 --> 00:12:27,140
I've hired a bargainer in secret to secure a spot for me.

147
00:12:27,140 --> 00:12:29,010
I'm signing the contract tomorrow.

148
00:12:29,010 --> 00:12:31,740
- So you're the one who hired the bargainer?
- Yes.

149
00:12:31,740 --> 00:12:33,860
Your brother will be pissed off if he knows about it!

150
00:12:33,860 --> 00:12:39,390
I know! So I'm counting on you, Brother Hebo, to say something nice for me.

151
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:41,780
Please, Brother Hebo.

152
00:12:43,050 --> 00:12:44,670
Okay, okay. I got it.

153
00:12:44,670 --> 00:12:47,050
You're the best, Brother Hebo!

154
00:12:47,050 --> 00:12:49,350
Come, have a seat.

155
00:12:49,350 --> 00:12:52,550
You should talk to your brother more often.

156
00:12:52,550 --> 00:12:57,020
He's not unreasonable. He cares too much about you, and he is afraid that you will be hurt.

157
00:12:57,020 --> 00:12:59,920
I know. I'll find a time to have a good chat with him.

158
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:04,430
- Oh, I almost forgot.
- What?

159
00:13:04,430 --> 00:13:08,970
Congratulations on your promotion, Brother Hebo!

160
00:13:08,970 --> 00:13:10,160
You’ve been blowing your money again?

161
00:13:10,160 --> 00:13:13,760
Not at all! I know Brother Hebo doesn't like it when I spend frivolously.

162
00:13:13,760 --> 00:13:17,200
I've made them by myself. Do they look nice?

163
00:13:19,430 --> 00:13:21,500
- Really? Did you really make them by yourself?
- Yeah.

164
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:23,680
Do you like them, Brother Hebo?

165
00:13:25,590 --> 00:13:26,700
Yes.

166
00:13:26,700 --> 00:13:29,580
I'm glad you like them!

167
00:13:29,580 --> 00:13:33,450
I'll be heading home. Zhijuan is waiting for me at home.

168
00:13:33,450 --> 00:13:36,350
See you. Brother Hebo, bye!

169
00:13:36,350 --> 00:13:38,300
- Take care.
- Will do.

170
00:13:52,020 --> 00:13:54,790
Assistant An, I've arrived at Evergreen.

171
00:13:54,790 --> 00:14:00,390
The representative of Xinyuan Technology has not arrived yet. Maybe you can wait for him in the meeting room.

172
00:14:00,390 --> 00:14:02,330
Is that the case?

173
00:14:02,670 --> 00:14:04,800
Okay, I got it.

174
00:14:07,850 --> 00:14:09,570
Xia Qian.

175
00:14:24,280 --> 00:14:25,640
What's up?

176
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:27,680
Can we talk?

177
00:14:30,850 --> 00:14:32,580
He Zhijuan.

178
00:14:39,810 --> 00:14:42,240
I've got other stuff to deal with.

179
00:14:42,240 --> 00:14:44,380
Just say what you want.

180
00:14:45,150 --> 00:14:47,180
I hope that you can terminate Mengmeng's contract with you.

181
00:14:47,180 --> 00:14:49,690
About this...

182
00:14:49,690 --> 00:14:53,760
you should talk to your fiancée, not me.

183
00:14:55,160 --> 00:14:59,110
She doesn't know about it. And I don't want her to know.

184
00:14:59,110 --> 00:15:01,960
I wasn't planning on telling her about it.

185
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:05,340
So you ran away from our engagement ceremony

186
00:15:05,340 --> 00:15:08,030
because of Ning Meng?

187
00:15:08,980 --> 00:15:13,610
It had nothing to do with her. I just realized on the engagement day that I didn't love you anymore.

188
00:15:13,610 --> 00:15:16,290
I couldn't force myself to be with you.

189
00:15:16,290 --> 00:15:19,960
You realized that you didn't love me on the engagement day?

190
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:21,200
You realized it pretty early.

191
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:24,660
Xia Qian, can you not be sarcastic?

192
00:15:24,660 --> 00:15:27,880
There's no such rule that I can only love one person in my life.

193
00:15:36,990 --> 00:15:39,880
I've known you for such a long time,

194
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:43,070
and this is the first time I've realized that you've taken things so easy.

195
00:15:50,400 --> 00:15:54,690
I know you need money these days. There's ¥100,000 on this card.

196
00:15:54,690 --> 00:15:56,890
I want you to give up your job.

197
00:15:56,890 --> 00:16:00,240
Mengmeng doesn't know anything about us yet.

198
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:02,240
We haven't met in two years, but I don't think that's a long time.

199
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:04,380
You forgot who I am?

200
00:16:04,380 --> 00:16:06,330
It's true that I'm poor and I need money.

201
00:16:06,330 --> 00:16:09,440
But I'm not that pathetic to take money from you!

202
00:16:10,430 --> 00:16:12,460
I repeat. Rest assured,

203
00:16:12,460 --> 00:16:15,190
I won't tell Ning Meng what happened between us.

204
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:23,130
If it were possible, I wish I never had anything to do with you.

205
00:16:23,130 --> 00:16:27,220
Just take your hush money back. I don't need it.

206
00:16:30,650 --> 00:16:32,460
Anything else?

207
00:16:34,390 --> 00:16:36,980
If you can terminate this contract,

208
00:16:36,980 --> 00:16:39,200
I'll satisfy whatever requests you make.

209
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:43,650
Think of it as my compensation for hurting you emotionally.

210
00:16:43,650 --> 00:16:47,010
Compensation for hurting me? How?

211
00:16:47,010 --> 00:16:49,180
Who do you think you are?

212
00:16:49,180 --> 00:16:53,330
And I’m over what happened between us a long time ago.

213
00:16:55,470 --> 00:16:57,250
Anything else?

214
00:17:00,260 --> 00:17:02,180
Xia Qian.

215
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:23,580
[Xia Qian]

216
00:17:40,830 --> 00:17:43,860
Brother, this is my boyfriend Zhijuan.

217
00:17:43,860 --> 00:17:46,510
Nice to meet you, I'm He Zhijuan.

218
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:46,550
Thank you.

219
00:18:52,630 --> 00:18:55,520
Did you hear what we were talking about?

220
00:19:03,630 --> 00:19:05,790
I'm feeling sad now,

221
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:09,270
not because I'm still in love with him.

222
00:19:10,830 --> 00:19:13,750
It's because it's hard for me to accept the truth of why he left me.

223
00:19:13,750 --> 00:19:16,140
Do you know how overboard he went?

224
00:19:17,150 --> 00:19:20,490
Two years ago, he ran away

225
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:22,620
from our engagement ceremony.

226
00:19:22,620 --> 00:19:25,480
Why would he run away?

227
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:28,240
I've been thinking about it for two years.

228
00:19:31,190 --> 00:19:34,880
I was even wondering if he had some kind of terminal disease

229
00:19:34,880 --> 00:19:38,210
and couldn't be cured, and he left me because he was afraid I'd be sad.

230
00:19:38,210 --> 00:19:41,800
But in the end, this is what the truth is.

231
00:19:41,800 --> 00:19:44,840
He just didn't like me anymore.

232
00:19:44,840 --> 00:19:47,190
But it's okay.

233
00:19:47,190 --> 00:19:50,030
I don't care about it anymore now.

234
00:19:50,030 --> 00:19:52,000
I'm so sorry.

235
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:55,580
I've said so much nonsense to you.

236
00:19:55,580 --> 00:19:57,480
Sorry for wasting your time.

237
00:19:57,480 --> 00:20:01,530
I've been using this handkerchief. I'll wash it and give it back to you tomorrow.

238
00:20:06,400 --> 00:20:07,720
Excuse me.

239
00:20:07,730 --> 00:20:11,110
Miss Xia, the agent is waiting in the meeting room. Where are you?

240
00:20:11,120 --> 00:20:13,660
Oh. Just a moment, I'll be right there.

241
00:20:13,660 --> 00:20:15,660
Okay. See you soon.

242
00:20:16,990 --> 00:20:19,360
I've got something urgent to deal with. I'll be on my way.

243
00:20:19,360 --> 00:20:22,480
Thank you. I'll give it back to you tomorrow.

244
00:20:39,460 --> 00:20:40,950
- Hello?
 - Hello, Brother.

245
00:20:40,950 --> 00:20:42,780
Are you free tonight?

246
00:20:42,780 --> 00:20:47,580
I want to invite you over for dinner and... have a chat with you.

247
00:20:48,770 --> 00:20:50,890
I need to talk to you, too.

248
00:20:50,890 --> 00:20:54,180
That's great. I'll see you tonight!

249
00:21:03,330 --> 00:21:06,460
Brother! You've brought so much delicious food for me!

250
00:21:06,460 --> 00:21:10,090
I'll make dinner first, and then we can eat and talk together.

251
00:21:16,060 --> 00:21:18,630
That's delicious! These are all my favorites!

252
00:21:18,630 --> 00:21:19,810
Have a seat.

253
00:21:19,810 --> 00:21:22,280
I need to talk to you about something.

254
00:21:34,150 --> 00:21:35,970
Zhijuan! Come on in!

255
00:21:35,970 --> 00:21:39,070
My brother made a lot of delicious food for us!

256
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:44,010
Brother.

257
00:21:44,010 --> 00:21:45,860
Brother Zhening.

258
00:21:47,090 --> 00:21:49,780
There's one more dish. You guys can sit first.

259
00:21:53,290 --> 00:21:56,150
My brother is slow to warm up. It'll get better.

260
00:21:56,150 --> 00:21:58,640
- Okay.
- Have a seat.

261
00:22:06,500 --> 00:22:09,140
Brother, I've mentioned to you before

262
00:22:09,140 --> 00:22:10,710
that Zhijuan is super good.

263
00:22:10,710 --> 00:22:15,270
He's the best and the youngest psychiatrist in his clinic.

264
00:22:15,270 --> 00:22:19,960
And he's very gentle and considerate.

265
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:21,950
Everyone is envious of me.

266
00:22:21,950 --> 00:22:25,370
They said I've found the perfect man for myself the first attempt at love.

267
00:22:25,370 --> 00:22:28,900
Mengmeng, you're overstating it.

268
00:22:28,900 --> 00:22:31,320
I should have let you meet with my brother earlier.

269
00:22:31,320 --> 00:22:34,450
He'd know how great you are.

270
00:22:35,350 --> 00:22:37,900
I'm full, enjoy the meal you two.

271
00:22:44,910 --> 00:22:49,030
The fish my brother made is really delicious. Have some more.

272
00:22:52,470 --> 00:22:54,400
Eat more.

273
00:22:57,530 --> 00:23:00,340
- You don't have to see me out.
- I do!

274
00:23:02,370 --> 00:23:05,300
Zhijuan, my brother is not like that usually.

275
00:23:05,300 --> 00:23:07,880
Please don't be mad.

276
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:11,420
It's okay. If I had a sister as lovely as you,

277
00:23:11,420 --> 00:23:14,490
I'd be unhappy if she brings her boyfriend home.

278
00:23:16,290 --> 00:23:18,400
I'll go downstairs with you.

279
00:23:18,400 --> 00:23:20,140
It's okay.

280
00:23:21,320 --> 00:23:24,280
- I'll be leaving now.
- Take care!

281
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:36,770
Brother, why are you putting on a long face?

282
00:23:36,770 --> 00:23:39,930
