283
00:23:39,930 --> 00:23:41,790
Are you the one who hired Xia Qian

284
00:23:41,790 --> 00:23:44,070
to get the wedding reservation?

285
00:23:46,540 --> 00:23:49,740
You know that I don't want you to get married so early.

286
00:23:49,740 --> 00:23:53,940
So you're thinking to act first and ask later?

287
00:23:53,940 --> 00:23:56,890
I just want to get married to him right away!

288
00:23:56,890 --> 00:23:59,590
How long have you guys been dating? Do you really know him?

289
00:23:59,590 --> 00:24:01,250
How would I not?

290
00:24:01,250 --> 00:24:03,450
When I saw him, at first sight,

291
00:24:03,450 --> 00:24:07,070
