294
00:24:12,110 --> 00:24:15,060
I just love him. I just want to marry him.

295
00:24:15,060 --> 00:24:17,900
Even if I'm infatuated, I'd still be willing to do that.

296
00:24:29,110 --> 00:24:32,720
