297
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:36,340
I think Mr. He loves Miss Ning Meng a lot.

298
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:41,050
How long does love last?

299
00:24:41,050 --> 00:24:43,780
To see if a man

300
00:24:43,780 --> 00:24:45,540
can hold onto his marriage,

301
00:24:45,540 --> 00:24:48,660
