303
00:24:51,290 --> 00:24:54,120
from his engagement ceremony because of love,

304
00:24:54,120 --> 00:24:58,140
then couldn't he leave Mengmeng for someone else?

305
00:24:58,140 --> 00:25:00,570
How can I rest assured if Mengmeng is married to

306
00:25:00,570 --> 00:25:03,570
a man like him with no sense of responsibility?

307
00:25:04,710 --> 00:25:06,900
Makes sense.

308
00:25:06,900 --> 00:25:09,030
Then, what do we do about Miss Xia?

309
00:25:09,030 --> 00:25:11,770
