312
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:42,970
Tell me why.

313
00:25:42,970 --> 00:25:45,880
I have my own reasons and I don't have to explain them to you.

314
00:25:45,880 --> 00:25:50,430
By the way, here's all your reward

315
00:25:50,430 --> 00:25:52,650
for bargaining for Evergreen.

316
00:25:55,030 --> 00:25:58,310
I don't want money. I want the reservation for the wedding in May.

317
00:25:58,310 --> 00:26:00,370
Then there's nothing for us to discuss.

318
00:26:00,370 --> 00:26:02,050
You've gone back on your words, do you know?

319
00:26:02,050 --> 00:26:07,260
