386
00:32:08,050 --> 00:32:10,250
But the key is that we need to get the list first.

387
00:32:10,250 --> 00:32:12,940
We're not spies.

388
00:32:17,140 --> 00:32:20,080
I've got a plan.

389
00:32:20,080 --> 00:32:23,540
This is your first day at work. Your probation is three months.

390
00:32:23,540 --> 00:32:25,220
If you want to stay at Evergreen,

391
00:32:25,220 --> 00:32:27,190
