392
00:32:27,190 --> 00:32:29,580
- Is that clear?
- Yes!

393
00:32:29,580 --> 00:32:31,750
Good. Get to your work.

394
00:32:32,860 --> 00:32:36,580
[Sheng Zhening]

395
00:32:36,580 --> 00:32:38,650
[Xia Qian]

396
00:32:40,710 --> 00:32:43,430
Miss Xia, now that you've signed the contract,

397
00:32:43,430 --> 00:32:46,730
I assume you've agreed to give up on the wedding reservation?

398
00:32:46,730 --> 00:32:49,520
It's over and we're partners now.

399
00:32:49,520 --> 00:32:52,590
Yeah, sure. All the best to our collaboration.

400
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:58,920
Is there...

401
00:32:58,920 --> 00:33:01,540
Do you have any concerns?

402
00:33:02,670 --> 00:33:03,970
No.

403
00:33:03,970 --> 00:33:05,520
We've signed the contract.

404
00:33:05,520 --> 00:33:09,120
I'll do my best to do whatever I've promised you, GM Sheng.

405
00:33:11,140 --> 00:33:13,470
Anything else? I'll be on my way if there's nothing else.

406
00:33:13,470 --> 00:33:16,830
Just a moment. I have a little bit of doubt.

407
00:33:16,830 --> 00:33:19,560
Before, I felt that

408
00:33:19,560 --> 00:33:24,050
you were not so willing to take on the car bargaining order, but why all of a sudden...?

409
00:33:24,050 --> 00:33:28,500
For money's sake. Who doesn't like money?

410
00:33:28,500 --> 00:33:30,930
And people should be flexible.

411
00:33:30,930 --> 00:33:35,520
Evergreen will give you a satisfactory reward for sure.

412
00:33:35,520 --> 00:33:37,600
Thank you, GM Sheng.

413
00:33:38,620 --> 00:33:40,480
This copy is yours.

414
00:33:41,300 --> 00:33:44,280
I have a very busy schedule these days,

415
00:33:44,280 --> 00:33:47,100
